snippet.title: HackeRPG - First Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
First gameplay trailer of HackeRPG - action roguelike for coders! Fight viruses, bugs and trojans using your coding skills.

Early access in the Steam will start soon.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2671770/HackeRPG/
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/hackerpg/
Discord: https://discord.gg/Gzu4YPJXyx
